    "body": "Makes sense, but shouldn't AtomicPtr have T: Sized? [1] Presumably this check is currently implemented with compiler magic, but it would be nice to have it explicit in the API.\n\n[1] https://doc.rust-lang.org/std/sync/atomic/struct.AtomicPtr.html\n",
