    "updated_at": "2016-09-27T00:21:33Z",
    "body": "Right, I get that - I'm suggesting that we make that constraint explicit in the API [1], since currently the |T| in |AtomicPtr<T>| is not constrained to be |Sized|.\n\n[1] https://doc.rust-lang.org/std/sync/atomic/struct.AtomicPtr.html\n",
